title: Agent restart during graceful restart/drain is being fed into generic retry logic as Agent.Restart_requested, causing pointless retry attempts during shutdown handoff. Treat restart-requested as a control-flow outcome, not a retriable failure.
---

Agent restart during graceful restart/drain is being fed into generic retry logic as Agent.Restart_requested, causing pointless retry attempts during shutdown handoff. Treat restart-requested as a control-flow outcome, not a retriable failure.
